<section class="faq-section" aria-labelledby="faq-heading">
  <div style="max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 28px">
    <h2 id="faq-heading">Madurai Software Development — FAQs</h2>
    <p class="faq-sub">Common questions Madurai SMEs ask before signing up.</p>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Do you have a Madurai office?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">Softwaller is headquartered in Salem and serves Madurai through dedicated on-site implementation visits, video calls and remote support. Salem to Madurai is roughly 3.5 hours by road via NH 44 and NH 38, so our consultants travel to Madurai for kickoff workshops, training and go-live support. Most Madurai SMEs do not need a local vendor office because we bundle scheduled visits into every project.</div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Can the jewellery software fetch live gold rate?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">Yes. Our jewellery billing software pulls daily 22K and 24K gold and silver rates from configurable rate sources or your bullion association feed and auto-updates billing prices. Staff can override rates per invoice with audit logging. The software also handles wastage, making charges, hallmark HUID tracking, RFID stock counting, BIS-compliant invoicing and exchange of old gold.</div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Do you support Tamil interface?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">Yes. We deliver bilingual user interfaces with English plus Tamil labels for shop floor, billing counter and warehouse modules. Invoice prints, SMS templates and WhatsApp Business messages can be configured in Tamil for end customers. Training is delivered in Tamil for billing staff and stockroom users, and in English for owners and accountants.</div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>How is custom clinic software different from generic HMS?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">Generic hospital management systems are built for 200-bed multi-specialty hospitals. Madurai single-doctor clinics, dental practices and small diagnostic labs need lighter software focused on OPD queue, appointment booking, prescription printing, ABHA ID linking under the Ayushman Bharat Digital Mission and a simple billing module. Our custom clinic software delivers exactly these workflows without forcing you into modules you will never use.</div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>What does WhatsApp Business setup cost in Madurai?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">WhatsApp Business API setup with Softwaller starts at around Rs 25,000 one-time for Meta verification, template approval and integration with your CRM or booking system. Monthly conversation charges follow Meta's published per-conversation rates and depend on your message volume. Service and utility conversations cost less than marketing conversations. We share a fixed estimate after understanding your message use cases.</div>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

